{
  "doc_id": "4774",
  "text": "Gene Ontology (GO) term analysis for 355 genes was performed using FuncAssociate 2.0. [CITATION_1] The gene list was compiled of probable sRNA targets; 297 mRNAs, 4 intra-5′ UTR-RNAs and 54 ig-5′ UTR-RNAs. As a background set (gene space) all genes from our annotation set were used. Significantly enriched GO terms were identified by applying an adjusted p-value cutoff of 0.05.",
